Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.53,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}无限远点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:49.03,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}不过是个 价值观被改写
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:52.33,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}普通的平行世界
