Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:15.86,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}只缘我能飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.55,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}那一瞬间 那些场面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.15,op-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}对你来说 如果很特别
