Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:07.45,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be2}Orbit of photon and universe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:13.68,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be2}I am just the part of its plan
